Nso (Lamnso, Lamnsɔ́́) bụ asụsụ Grassfields nkè ndị Nso nkè ọdịda anyanwụ Cameroon
Mmadụ olé na ole nwere ike ịnọgide na Naịjirịa
O nwere klas irí dị mkpa. Koodu ISO 639-3 bụ lns. Ìhè karịrị 100,000 mmadụ na-asụ Nso.
Nso na-eji orthography dabere ná General Alphabet of Cameroon Languages (AGLC)
E mepụtara orthography ná mbụ tupu á gbanwee yá iji soro aro nkè AGLC
Ọ na-eji digraphs irí abụọ ná  atọ, dz, gb, gh, gv, gw, jw, kf, kp, kw, mb, mf, mf, mt, mv, nj, ns, nt, ny, bg,表演, ŋw, sh, ts, ná trigraphs asaa
Mkpụrụedemede ogologo na-egosi site ná okpukpu abụọ nkè ụdaume bụ ːa, ee, əə, ii, oo, uu
Á na-edepụta Diphthongs na-akpọ, ey, əy, oy, uy, iy.
Á na-egosi ụda dị élú ná ụda ólú dị élú ná ólú dị ala ná ụda ólú siri ike nà ụdaume.
